The home page will have nav links for 
home, about, FAQ, stock, movie. 
Put the nav in your layout.html.erb file. Include some text on the about and FAQ pages.
 
When you click on the stock page, there is a form to input a ticker symbol. 
The next page shows the ticker symbol and its current trading price. 
Hint: There is a function called number_to_currency(). 
Google it and use it.
 
When you click on the movie page, there is a form to input a movie title. 
The next page shows the movie poster and some other info for the movie.
 
You have to put any gem you want to use in your Gemfile. 
You have to run bundle anytime you change your Gemfile. 
Your rails server needs to be restarted after any changes to your Gemfile. 
